Description.Text: The Wellington Hotel is located on Seventh Avenue at the corner of 55th Street, one short block from Broadway, Carnegie Hall and City Center. Central Park is just four blocks away and Rockefeller Center is seven blocks from the hotel. La Guardia Airport is 10 miles from the Wellington Hotel.

Carnegie Hall - 1 block Central Park - 4 blocks Museum of Modern Art - 4 blocks Rockefeller Center - 7 blocks Times Square - 8 blocks Lincoln Center - 9 blocks Museum of Natural History - 1.5 miles Metropolitan Museum of Art - 1.5 miles

The 27-story Wellington has 600 guestrooms and suites. All offer wireless Internet access (surcharge), cable TV with pay movies, and telephones with voice mail and data ports. Suites have kitchenettes. Other amenities include iron/ironing boards and hair dryers. Air condition is offered seasonally. Decor is traditional, with dark-wood furniture, swagged curtains, and lightly striped wall coverings. Bathrooms have shower/tub combinations. Wireless Internet access is available in all guestrooms (surcharge).

Décor in the 600 guestrooms and suites includes dark wood furnishings and traditional accents. All accommodations feature high- speed Internet access and cable television. The Art Deco lobby features high-ceilings, an inviting marble fireplace and a sitting area under a large crystal chandelier. The lobby features a computer with high-speed Internet access for a fee.

Central Park, three blocks to the north, offers walking, biking, and running paths; in-line and ice-skating; birding; boating; and a host of other recreational diversions. With the famous Christmas tree sparkling above it, the Rink at Rockefeller Plaza—six blocks from the hotel—is a special treat during the winter holiday season.
Check In Time - 3 p.m. Check Out Time - 12 p.m.

Driving directions from LaGuardia Airport: Take Grand Central Parkway W to I-278 W (Brooklyn-Queens Expressway). Exit to SR 25A and bear right onto Queens Plaza N. Take the Queensboro Bridge and exit onto Second Ave. Head south, then turn right onto East 57th St. Turn left onto Seventh Ave. The hotel entrance is on the left just before West 55th Street.

This hotel provides beauty services, two restaurants. The Park Cafe, a neighborhood gem, serves coffee and light fare late into the evening. The award-winning Molyvos, a Mediterranean restaurant, features Greek and other Mediterranean specialties.
